extends ../main-layout

block headAppendTitle
    title TJ Tech - System Development

block content
    .container.pt-5.crm-service.system-development
        .row
            .col-12.col-xl-3
                .text-intro.text-nowrap.mt-5 We Build Trust
                .text-intro-explain.text-mt.text-nowrap With All Our Fintech Solutions
                .button-mb-center
                    a(href="contact.html")
                        button.btn-base.learn-btn Learn More
            .col-12.col-xl-9
                img(style='width: 100%;' src='assets/images/p_ecosystem.svg' alt='')
        .g-header.text-center.head-spacing System Development
        .row.leading
            .coml-first-img
                img(src="assets/images/sys_development.png", alt="")
        .descriptor-item.d-flex.align-items-start
            img(src='assets/images/ic_mini_rounded_tick.svg' alt='')
            .detail TJ Tech offers a comprehensive solution for businesses looking to develop custom software applications to meet their specific needs. A team of business analysts and highly experienced developers work closely with clients to understand their requirements and create software solutions that are tailored to their unique needs. The customisation range can vary from website interface (from which our clients can choose layout), the appearance of their administrator pages, users pages, IB settings, MAM and PAMM settings, or installing any other add-on or plugin.
        .descriptor-item.d-flex.align-items-start.my-4
            img(src='assets/images/ic_mini_rounded_tick.svg' alt='')
            .detail A wide range of other services, including software design, development, testing, and maintenance. The development process is flexible and agile, ensuring that TJ Tech can adapt to changing requirements and deliver high-quality software on time and within budget.
        .row.leading
            .descriptor.col-12.col-lg-7
                .descriptor-item.d-flex.align-items-start
                    img(src='assets/images/ic_mini_rounded_tick.svg' alt='')
                    .detail TJ Tech is proud of its commitment to 100% customer satisfaction - working closely with clients throughout the development process to ensure that their needs are being met and that the final product exceeds their expectations.
                .descriptor-item.d-flex.align-items-start.mt-4
                    img(src='assets/images/ic_mini_rounded_tick.svg' alt='')
                    .detail Whether you need a custom software application developed from scratch, or want to improve an existing system, TJ Tech development service can help! Contact the team today to learn more about the services and how you can be helped to achieve your business goals through software development.
            .figure.col-12.col-lg-5.coml-none
                .image-shadow.right
                img.main-image(src='assets/images/sys_development.png' alt='' style='width: 408 px;')

